<br>
The most difficult thing i've tanked is the Black Dire in Mistmoore.  It has a fair amount of hp, decent MR, and hits for up to 200.  I was the only melee present at the battle.  Sung haste(50%+str+atk), slow(32%+lowerAC+lowerAgi), debuffed MR(and DoT) so i could land slow, and clicked BoH(7hp per tick+7str).<br>
<br>
